<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>331</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Vawlei khua zakip ah, Ka Bawi Jesuh he, Keimah cu him tein ka kal
 zungzal ko, Amah loin khuazei hmanh ah kaa lawm lo, A um ahcun khua
 zeihmanh ah ka tih lo.

[C1]
   Khua zeihmanh ah, Jesuh thawngin ka him ko. Khuazei hmanh, Khua
   zeihmanh, Zeihmanh ka phang lo.

[V2]
 Jesuh a um tikah ka van a sang lo, Ka kawi a ka hlaw nain Jesuh um ko,
 A harbik lam chungah khan, Phan hmanh ning law, Jesuh he ka um ahcun
 zungzal kaa lawm.

[C2]
   Khua zeihmanh ah, Jesuh thawngin ka him ko. Khuazei hmanh, Khua
   zeihmanh, Zeihmanh ka phang lo.

[V3]
 Khua zeihmanh ah thihnak caan kha cu ning law, Vancung khua ah, Jesuh
 a ka kalpi lai, Vawlei lam har chungah ka chuak than lai lo, Khuazei
 hmanh ah Jesuh he ka hna ngam ko.

[C3]
   Khua zeihmanh ah, Jesuh thawngin ka him ko. Khuazei hmanh, Khua
   zeihmanh, Zeihmanh ka phang lo.</lyrics>
<key>D</key>
<title>VAWLEI KHUAZAKIP AH JESUH HE CH331</title>
</song>